<problem id="fs-idm380610592">
<para id="fs-idm375457424"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68084"/>Extreme Sports sells logo sports merchandise. The company is contemplating whether or not to continue its custom embroidery service. All of the company’s direct fixed costs can be avoided if a segment is dropped. This information is available for the segments.</para>
